            "title": "A股午後挫約1%  DeepSeek概念退潮",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股午後逾1%，創業板指數跌近2%，DeepSeek概念整體瀉逾一成。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指全日跌31點或0.93%，報3324點，今早以3348點開市，跌6點或0.2%，全日最高見3366點，升11點或0.33%，下午市況回調，低見3314點，跌41點或1.22%，全日成交3324.49億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指全日報10617，跌173點或1.61%，今早開市報10781點，亦跌9點或0.09%，最高見10817，升26點或0.24%，下午顯著回調，最低見10577，跌214點或1.98%，全日成交11023.12億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數全日收報3912，跌34點或0.88%，今早跌4點或0.12%，開報3942點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數全日跌44點或1.98%，報2182點，今早開市報2223點，跌3點或0.14%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深DeepSeek概念退潮，夢網科技(002123.SZ)挫10.02%，報18.51元、美格智能(002881.SZ)跌9.97%，報54.25元、泛微網絡(603039.SH)跌10%，報71.91元、杭鋼股份(600126.SH)跌9.96%，永信至誠(688244.SH)跌9.98%，報46元、佳發教育(300559.SZ)瀉11.66%，報13.34元、通達海(301378.SZ)跌11.14%，報33.97元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14714879-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e6%8c%ab%e7%b4%841-deepseek%e6%a6%82%e5%bf%b5%e9%80%80%e6%bd%ae",
